Text:
The description for this release is incorrect. This was never released before in this format. It is a compilation of songs released from 1981 to 1989. I have never heard of Anna Logue Records.

Glad you like it. I recorded it. I am/was webeecho. Now recording as LivingWithAnAngel.
You are quite right sir. I relooked at my sources and mistook it prior. It was linked offa Anna logue records somehow, so I assumed it was by them. It is off of Vinyl on Demand. Great works indeed.
